casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Preston, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Preston (1990), 52 Ohio St. 3d 270.]

(No. 89-1814 Submitted May 29, 1990 Decided July 25, 1990.) Appeal from the Court of Appeals for Clermont County, No. CA89-04-027. Donald W. White, prosecuting attorney, and Timothy E. Schneider, for appellant. W. Stephen Haynes, for appellee.

This case is reversed and remanded on authority of State v. Chippendale (1990), 52 Ohio St. 3d 118, 556 N.E. 2d 1134.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and Resnick, JJ., concur. H. Brown, J., dissents.
